## Interface: 30300
## Title: COA State Plates - Enemy
## Notes: The "I care about enemy plates" surface for COA State Plates: loading this addon ATTACHES the core's enemy-plate machinery (threat coloring, mob aggro cue, instance fill - all inert in the core without this) and adds its config page under Interface > AddOns. Disable this addon and the core returns to baseline for enemy plates.
